author: Alywin_Incomplete_Sets
title: All about doors and windows
review:
This set is what you can see, all windows and doors.  The parts are old-style, but still very useful.  The colour theme, being red supplemented with white and green, is in line with typical houses in Town and City series.

Overall speaking, this set is good for MOC and expansion of your town houses, but has not much value on a stand-alone basis.
